[[File:KiblaGreens.jpg|200px|thumb|Kibla greens]]
'''Kibla greens''' were nutritious vegetables regarded as flavorful by many in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. They could be found on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Dantooine/Legends|Dantooine]].<ref name="SWG">{{GalaxiesNGE}}</ref> [[Klaus Vandangante/Legends|Klaus Vandangante]] found kibla greens to be rather unpalatable as a seven-year-old child, and he reprogrammed the [[Droid/Legends|droid]] nanny to discard them in a vase in the family living room, along with [[flangth]] and [[stewed gwouch]].<ref name="HSSB">''[[Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Kibla greens were created for an offhand mention in the entry on [[Klaus Vandangante/Legends|Klaus Vandangante]] in the ''[[Han Solo and the Corporate Sector Sourcebook]]'', authored by [[Michael Allen Horne]] and published in [[November]] [[1993]] by [[West End Games]]. They would not be mentioned again until the creation of the [[Wikipedia:Massively multiplayer online role-playing game|massively multiplayer online roleplaying game]] ''[[Star Wars Galaxies]]''.

